This paper is primarily focused on video object detection, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) domain. The paper also introduces a novel recurrent computation unit (STMM) and a module to align spatial-temporal memory (MatchTrans), which are both related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates its method on a benchmark dataset (ImageNet VID), which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) applications.
